  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd: \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Evacuation of protestors: Police spokesperson statement",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police Media Spokesperson, Senior Superintendent of Police Advocate Nihal Taltuwa said that the people who had gathered in front of the Presidential Secretariat were not expected to leave.",
        "He said this during a special press conference held today (23) at the Government Information Department.",
        "He also said that he has the responsibility to release the Presidential Secretariat, which is seen as the main office structure for making decisions for the public, after being appointed by the President. (a)"
      ],
